    <item>
      <title>庞氏骗局爆发后，土耳其提议限制银行首席执行官任期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/turkey-proposes-limit-on-bank-ceo-tenures-after-ponzi-scandal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其银行业监管机构制定了一项计划，旨在限制银行高管的任期，此前，一家银行的首席执行官被指控涉嫌庞氏骗局，该银行是该国任职时间最长的银行之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/turkey-proposes-limit-on-bank-ceo-tenures-after-ponzi-scandal</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 12:18:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着负电价现象加剧，德国电价跌至零以下</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/german-power-slips-below-zero-as-negative-price-phenomenon-grows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国电价在年初的第一个交易日跌至零以下，随着可再生能源的扩张，这种现象在欧洲越来越常见。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/german-power-slips-below-zero-as-negative-price-phenomenon-grows</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 12:08:11 GMT</pubDate>
